{"tid":1692464,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"【幫手睇】示 威 現 場 驚 現 義 士 靈 體","createTime":"2019-11-04T05:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T03:35:32.000Z","uid":177082,"like":60,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"31953185cd3cdc0b3c5def4554532e0c827ca281","tid":1692464,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:45:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VQnKjhCZKUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVQnKjhCZKUw&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=9c68d780\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VQnKjhCZKUw</a><br />\n1:15出現 建議由1:10開始睇<br />\n<br />\n現場只有記者 1:15嗰陣清晰有個黑衫男仔企係警察隔離 鏡頭一轉已經見唔到個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察見到黑衫後生仔 點會唔捉？記者如果當時見到佢 點會唔影實佢？<br />\n<br />\n1:06 個男仔已經係片到出現過<br />\n片入面其他人好似完全見佢唔到<br />\n如果唔係靈體 會係啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n我對呢啲嘢唔熟 啱啱有位長輩send俾我睇<br />\n求各位巴絲一齊研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警你地小心啲 <br />\n我地做鬼都一定返黎搵你地</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f63aed4b858e97a36a46d6de0d02f15dc0548fef","tid":1692464,"uid":177082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"推到有人認得個男仔為止"},{"pid":"58cb6ec03498a15ff684d2e41ca5105dadc0b674","tid":1692464,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2004e5082a13d5e95e47bc2c0ec8d5c28a4834a","tid":1692464,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd7508b407a18a6e6aac07d1ac936d7002e75f4","tid":1692464,"uid":177082,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:51:31.000Z","msg":"1:06 有個黑衫人影係記者後面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i